 ---
title: "Холбоо барих"
layout: "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro"
---

<section class="bg-blue-400 py-20">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold ">Холбоо барих</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg">Бидэнтэй холбогдохын тулд доорх маягтыг бөглөөрэй.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="contact" class="py-20 bg-gray-100 ">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-center">Маягт бөглөх</h2>
    <form action="#" method="POST" class="mt-8 space-y-6">
      <div>
        <label for="name" class="block text-lg font-semibold">Нэр</label>
        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required class="w-full p-4 mt-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg" placeholder="Таны нэр" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="email" class="block text-lg font-semibold">И-мэйл</label>
        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required class="w-full p-4 mt-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg" placeholder="Таны и-мэйл" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="message" class="block text-lg font-semibold">Мэдээ</label>
        <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required class="w-full p-4 mt-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg" placeholder="Таны асуулт эсвэл санал"></textarea>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <button type="submit" class="bg-blue-500 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-blue-600 transition">Илгээх</button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-blue-500 text-white py-20 text-center">
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Бидэнтэй холбогдох</h2>
  <p class="mt-4 text-lg">Бид танд туслахад бэлэн байна. Дэлгэрэнгүй мэдээллийг доорх холбоосоор авах боломжтой.</p>
  <a href="tel:+123456789" class="mt-8 inline-block text-white border border-white px-6 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-white hover:text-blue-500 transition">Утас: +1 234 567 89</a>
  <br />
  <a href="mailto:info@example.com" class="mt-4 inline-block text-white border border-white px-6 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-white hover:text-blue-500 transition">info@example.com</a>
</section>
